cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with sentiment analysis on product reviews, which is a common topic in natural language processing. It could also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as the task of identifying opinion targets is related to information retrieval. Additionally, the use of CRF as the base learner suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the mention of knowledge-based features and expanding domain knowledge suggests that it could also belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
